{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Shalva Gegia","author":"Shalva Gegia"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"272d3a3f-7487-5f70-9aed-2ca371949a6a","excerpt":"BookSwap is the convenient platform in Georgia for people, who wants to find, swap, sell or buy second-hand books. Swap/Sell second-hand books is quit actual inâ€¦","html":"<p>BookSwap is the convenient platform in Georgia for people, who wants to find, swap, sell or buy second-hand books.</p>\n<p>Swap/Sell second-hand books is quit actual in Tbilisi (Georgia).</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/dfffb590b352ba001a7435fffcec8c76/44154/logo.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 182px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 27.47252747252747%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"bookswap.ge\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/dfffb590b352ba001a7435fffcec8c76/44154/logo.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/dfffb590b352ba001a7435fffcec8c76/ff178/logo.png 148w,\n/static/dfffb590b352ba001a7435fffcec8c76/44154/logo.png 182w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 182px) 100vw, 182px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>Main idea, why I created BookSwap is that, the only way people could swap second-hand books in Tbilisi (Georgia) was though the Facebook Groups.</p>\n<p>I personally tried this types of groups/forums and had a conclusion: even though Facebook group served us well long time and helped interested people connect each other, I had feeling that and I missed some functionality I wanted.</p>\n<p>Facebook groups has its disadvantages, for example its impossible to make track of wanted book and get notified if someone sells or wants to swap it.</p>\n<p>Its hard to find/search desireable book though the wall of hundreds of posts.</p>\n<p>Thats why I created this side project called BookSwap.</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/43e3c4d92b594372a34e43e13533c3fa/f4374/web.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 60.9744094488189%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"bookswap.ge\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/43e3c4d92b594372a34e43e13533c3fa/fb8a0/web.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/43e3c4d92b594372a34e43e13533c3fa/1a291/web.png 148w,\n/static/43e3c4d92b594372a34e43e13533c3fa/2bc4a/web.png 295w,\n/static/43e3c4d92b594372a34e43e13533c3fa/fb8a0/web.png 590w,\n/static/43e3c4d92b594372a34e43e13533c3fa/526de/web.png 885w,\n/static/43e3c4d92b594372a34e43e13533c3fa/fa2eb/web.png 1180w,\n/static/43e3c4d92b594372a34e43e13533c3fa/08f6a/web.png 1770w,\n/static/43e3c4d92b594372a34e43e13533c3fa/f4374/web.png 4064w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>View on  <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/bookswap-georgia/id1440375612?ls=1&#x26;mt=8\">App Store</a>\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.bookswap.app\">Play Store</a></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"BookSwap - Convenient platform for swapping books","date":"Invalid date"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/bookswap/","previous":null,"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/about-me/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"About Me"}}}}